  "body": "\r\n---\r\n\r\nIf you've experienced a bug, please provide the following information:\r\n\r\n### Description of the Issue\r\n\r\nWhen I manually input a gas limit that is too low, the calculation of the equivalent price in USD isn't calculated, instead it shows that it is loading and fails to load even after waiting a long time. An error should be given instead of just loading forever.  (When gas limit is reasonable, the calculation of the equivalent price in USD is shown almost instantly)\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n1. Unlock wallet\r\n2. Go to advanced options for sending a transaction\r\n3. Input a low gas limit (keep gwei normal)\r\n\r\n### Description of Your Machine\r\n\r\nWindows 10, Chrome\r\n\r\n### Console Logs / Screenshots\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/25834495/39949916-f5d8ab0a-554b-11e8-8bee-91ffacb0ef3d.png)\r\n\r\n(Console logs or screenshots go here, if applicable)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/25834495/39949910-f04dce04-554b-11e8-9348-aed71b5e7be7.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nIf you're suggesting a feature, make sure someone hasn't already posted it. If\r\nno one has, please provide the following information:\r\n\r\n### Description of the Feature\r\n\r\n(Your description goes here)\r\n\r\n### Example(s) of Feature\r\n\r\n(If another product or app is doing this, please link it)\r\n",
